# MadGraph5 process card: Drell-Yan pp -> Z/gamma* -> l+l- (M > 50 GeV)
#
# Inclusive Drell-Yan production with dilepton invariant mass above 50 GeV.
# The mmll cut is applied via the run_card in the launch script.
# Additional jets come from the Pythia8 parton shower (LO + PS).
#
# CMS reference xsec: 6345.99 pb (FEWZ NNLO, SMP-22-017)
# MG5 LO will give a lower value (~5000 pb); use the CMS ref for normalization.
#
# Run with:
#   ./bin/mg5_aMC cards/DYJetsToLL_M-50_proc.dat

import model sm
define l+ = e+ mu+ ta+
define l- = e- mu- ta-
generate p p > l+ l-
output output/DYJetsToLL_M-50 -nojpeg
